3. `pq-no-deadline` golden args assume agent rephrases the existing question — harmless now, but could bite if arg-matching evals are added later

**All CLAUDE.md rules pass.** Test registration is exact-pattern match. `_write` function used correctly. JSON matches Python source. Regenerated files correctly sync to current Python EvalSet state.
